# SmartPockets Cursor Rules

@AGENTS.md

## Context

SmartPockets is a fintech app for credit card power users. It uses:
- Next.js 16 + React 19
- Convex with Ents ORM
- Clerk authentication
- Plaid for bank data
- UntitledUI component library

## Skills Available

Clerk and Vercel skills are installed in .agents/skills/
Convex skills are installed in .claude/skills/

## Architecture

See AGENTS.md for:
- Full schema documentation
- Convex Ents patterns
- Plaid integration flow
- Security requirements
- Common pitfalls
